text: Igenchekyar () is a rural locality (a village) in Utyakovsky Selsoviet, Gafuriysky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 107 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Krasnousolsky, 6 km from Utyakovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Gafuriysky District
title: Igenchekyar
